ICSA Election Results

President Elect of 2025, and Board of Directors of 2025-2027

Congratulations to Dr. Rong Chen on being elected as ICSA 2025 President-elect, and to Dr. Yuguo Chen, Dr. Haitao Chu, Dr. Xinping Cui, Dr. Yushi Liu, and Dr. Yuanjia Wang on being elected to ICSA Board of Directors. Thanks to our election committee chaired by Dr. Yichuan Zhao and all ICSA members who voted.

AWARDS

ICSA offers various awards to honor the significant achievement and contribution of members and support trainees and young researchers.

EVENTS

ICSA organizes meetings throughout the year. Connect with others, and learn from leading statistical experts.

PUBLICATIONS

ICSA produces a variety of publications to promote new developments and share ideas in the field of statistics

JOBS

Check out career offerings in our ICSA jobs listing. If you are an advertiser, learn how to advertise with us.

Get Involved

Get In

Take advantage of discounts on meetings, free access to our publications, career resources, and more by becoming an ICSA member!

Go Further

Network with some of the brightest minds in Statistics and stay up-to-date on current, important topics in your field by attending our events.

Give Back

Your donation will help us continue in our mission, allow us to make improvements, and fund awards for students and young researchers.
